Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.72,0:00:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The first thing I noticed that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.33,0:00:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,morning was the silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.24,0:00:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the silence of the vaults I
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.93,0:00:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.70,0:00:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Dance, calculated, built to hide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.31,0:00:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.36,0:00:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the good kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.02,0:00:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind that only exists in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,rooms where someone sleeps in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.22,0:00:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Noelia breathed slowly beside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.32,0:00:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.72,0:00:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Her hand curled up near her
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The way she'd slept ever since
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.48,0:00:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,she'd started sharing the bed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.95,0:00:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.62,0:00:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.04,0:00:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I was still counting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I got up without making a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.28,0:00:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The penthouse had thin blinds
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.99,0:00:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that filtered the light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.34,0:00:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,off Lake Michigan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.86,0:00:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And cast pale patches across the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.73,0:00:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,sheets.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.66,0:00:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Long and quiet like fingers of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.17,0:00:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,light that didn't want to wake
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.69,0:00:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.46,0:00:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I stood there for a second just
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.04,0:00:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Her chest rose and fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.78,0:00:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No tension in her shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.08,0:00:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No glinch in her jaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.16,0:00:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd seen Oelia sleep restlessly,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.26,0:00:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,dreaming about
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.18,0:00:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the altar,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.12,0:00:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,about Calvin, about the big
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.94,0:01:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,screen that showed my
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.36,0:01:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.78,0:01:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.46,0:01:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was domesticity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the word I'd never had
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,a reason to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And now it turned up all the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.93,0:01:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stuck to the smallest things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.70,0:01:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I put my shirt on in silence,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.45,0:01:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,rolled the sleeves to my elbows,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.86,0:01:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and went to the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.46,0:01:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The coffee brood quick with that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.67,0:01:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,strong smell that took over the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.81,0:01:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,whole hallway on cold days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I used the chance to set the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.67,0:01:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,sugar bowl beside her cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The way she liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Spoon already inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.14,0:01:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It was ridiculous how much
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.14,0:01:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,attention I paid to small
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.06,0:01:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.02,0:01:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Before her, I didn't even know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.72,0:01:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a right position for a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.54,0:01:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,sugar bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria was waiting for me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.84,0:01:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the car parked in the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,private garage when I came down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Armored.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.28,0:01:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.16,0:01:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The window opened just enough
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.52,0:01:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,for him to see me and tighten
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,his expression by two
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,millimeters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.06,0:01:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,His way of saying good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.06,0:01:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.00,0:01:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.98,0:01:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Already had some.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.08,0:01:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Lair.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange definition of a lie for
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,someone who only asked a
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,question.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I got into the passenger seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The meeting was early.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The casino's annex office was 20
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,minutes from the penthouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and Masimo had confirmed the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.10,0:02:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,night before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,For weeks I'd been negotiating
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the transfer of two casino
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.67,0:02:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,operations to entirely legal
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,management.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.62,0:02:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Every signed paper was a crack I
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,put in what I'd inherited from
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.96,0:02:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was the only thing that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.94,0:02:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,felt coherent since Noelia had
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,agreed to sleep at my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she know you're going to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the casino?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.56,0:02:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria asked as the garage gate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.14,0:02:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The street was still damp with
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,cold, black puddles reflecting
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.05,0:02:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the street lights that hadn't
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.67,0:02:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,gone off yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I said a regular meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It was worse than if he had.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew Daria's silence is well
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,enough to tell which frequency
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,each one weighed on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That one weighed on disapproval.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:02:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd promised her on the balcony
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:02:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,her hand in mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.26,0:03:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That I wouldn't lie anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And there I was, three months
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,later,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,shaving the truth around the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.23,0:03:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,edges just so I wouldn't worry
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a micro-ly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.86,0:03:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was harmless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It was exactly the kind of thing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.99,0:03:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd sworn I would never do
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I clenched my jaw and looked
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The casino's annex office had
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the discretion only old money
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,buys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark oak walls, low lamps, the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.49,0:03:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,thick carpet that muffled the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,sound of your own foot steps,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and the round table my father
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,had made before he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Massimo was already seated in
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the same brown suit as always,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.14,0:03:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and the smile of a man who felt
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.97,0:03:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,at home in any room I walked
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,into.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd brought Dolcey from the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Italian bakery in the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,neighborhood,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,wrapped in wax paper that still
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,held warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He pushed the bundle toward me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,when he saw me arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat son, your thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.28,0:03:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't lost weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother called yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:03:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Said your thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe her more than a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:03:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:03:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I sat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario stayed standing against
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoulder against the frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Watching with that stillness
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that made everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,uncomfortable,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,except me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The meeting lasted two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Massimo questioned, with
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,calculated gentleness,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the speed at which I'd been
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,legalizing the operations he
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,said he understood,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that he respected it, that he
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,saw in me the same courage he'd
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,seen in my father,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but that slow was better, that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the market spooked easily,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that man loyal to me might feel
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,betrayed if the transition was
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,abrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Every word of his came wrapped
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in affection.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That was how he always spoke to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That was how he'd spoken to me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.12,0:04:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I nodded at several points,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,disagreed at a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,When I left the room, the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,hallway was cold and smelled of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the coffee no one had drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And Dario caught up to me before
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I reached the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He raised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.64,0:04:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.92,0:04:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I got in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I checked the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Our still left before the end of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Noelia's shift at the hotel,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but the urge to have lunch with
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,her had come out of nowhere and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,stayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.94,0:05:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I told Dario to drive over
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.55,0:05:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I texted to let her know I was
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,on my way,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'd brought hunger and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She replied with an emoji I
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't describe,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but it made me smile alone in
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the backseat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The hotel still had that clean
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,morning smell when I came in
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,through the service door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Marble, flowers changed early.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The faint trace of floor wax.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I took the internal elevator up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,When the door is opened on the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.45,0:05:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,floor of the old vaults, I
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a maintenance crew in
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the hallway, a ladder leaning
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,against the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A broken seal on one of the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,steel doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The ceiling light flickered
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,faintly as if the whole floor
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,were waking up along with
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever had been kept in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The door was open.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.64,0:05:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It was one of the oldest vaults
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.43,0:05:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,in the building,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:05:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,from the days when the hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,still served as a private vault
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,for city families who didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,trust banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No one was authorized to open
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,anything there without three
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,signatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at the badge on the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,chest of the nearest employee,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,who authorized the opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked at me, hesitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.44,0:06:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The events manager sir, Miss
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I walked toward the vault room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The hallway seemed longer than
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,it had ever been.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,As if each step I took added
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,another half meter to the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd felt this exact sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The sensation of arriving too
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,late to something I didn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.06,0:06:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,was happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When I turned the corner, I saw
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,noelia standing near a little
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,table pushed against the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorai was beside her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Holding a yellowed paper
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,envelope in both hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,careful the way someone holds
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,something that might break
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And on top of the table, an old
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,tape machine turned slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The tape running between two
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,worn plastic reels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.96,0:06:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A voice came out of the machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the voice of a man I
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:07:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but I recognized the surname he
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,spoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It was mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The dust smelled of old paper
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and damp metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the smell of the vault
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd already been there three
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.67,0:07:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,times that week.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Always with the renovation plans
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in my hand and my head somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The last thing I expected was to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,find something real.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.92,0:07:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorai said, tapping the steel
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,door with the tip of her
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.53,0:07:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,clipboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If a literal skeleton shows up
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,inside this vault,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I'm quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I laughed half-heartedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It was one of those polite
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,laughs, just so I wouldn't ruin
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.65,0:07:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,my friend's joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorai was the only person who
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,still made me laugh before
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And I knew she could tell when
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the laugh came out hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't call me on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the kind of friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that doesn't need explaining to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The employee turned the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The door opened with a groan
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.75,0:07:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that sounded like years choked
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Metal contracted by time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,resisting until the last second.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside there was dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.48,0:07:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Three yellowed folders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A large cassette tape inside a
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:07:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,little plastic case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:07:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And an envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.28,0:08:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the envelope that stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a name typed on the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.49,0:08:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,front.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And taro cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt my blood dropped to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhere it wasn't supposed to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.37,0:08:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I stood still too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The metal smell got stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Or I got more motionless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell which.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorai looked at the envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Looked at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And stopped joking in the same
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.84,0:08:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my father's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.32,0:08:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She picked up the envelope
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,without asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I picked up the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a label stuck to the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,side of the case with a date on
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A date from before I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My hands were shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I told myself they weren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And I looked at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And they kept shaking just the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Completely ignoring what I
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,thought about the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There was an old machine in the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,room next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the kind that still used
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It had belonged to the hotel's
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,previous director.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And had never been taken off the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.31,0:08:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgotten between papers and an
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.56,0:08:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,astray no one used anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I carried the tape over there
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,without thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorai followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:08:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet for the first time in
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:08:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I slotted it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I pressed the button.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The tape rast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then came a long hiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You know who I am, Mr. Melvani.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never heard that adult
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd heard his voice calling me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,to breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.98,0:09:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Reading a children's book out
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Singing happy birthday with the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,wrong lyrics because he thought
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the right ones were boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never heard my father's
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,voice being the voice of a man
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It was him the same way the echo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,of my own voice on the answering
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,machine was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Unmustakable even without a
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Even without context.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.58,0:09:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I came because my family was
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,threatened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He was saying his voice too
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Like someone who'd rehearsed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.83,0:09:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,before walking into the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And because you're the only man
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,in this city who can make that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,threat small.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Another voice answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Old, patient, with a heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,accent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And the kind of calm that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't come from kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It asked for three names.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My father gave the three names.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I pressed the pause button.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I pressed it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:09:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The tape kept going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They went back to the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear it better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the second time I
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,already knew what was coming and
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.78,0:10:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I listened anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Unable to prepare myself for
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt a hand on my shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And it took me half a second to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,understand it was surreye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.40,0:10:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She was just there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The weight of her hand in the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,right place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.96,0:10:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The way a true friend stays.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.92,0:10:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When there's no word that fixes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That was when I noticed the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,third body in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I lifted my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.76,0:10:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Everin was standing in the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.32,0:10:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,doorway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,White shirt with the sleeves
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,rolled to his elbows.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,His broad shoulders filling the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand braised on the side of the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.93,0:10:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,door.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Eyes on me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,On surreye after.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,On the machine last.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the second he understood
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,what was playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw his jaw lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the way a man holds his
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,breath without knowing he's held
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,For three months I'd set his
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,surname like a caress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd laughed at him when he
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,signed papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd whispered against his neck
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:10:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,in the kitchen while the coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:10:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,brewed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:10:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd completely forgotten what
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that surname was capable of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The tape kept running.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's voice said the third
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,name again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear, without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,On a hotel floor that smelled of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And of something that shouldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,have been kept for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.16,0:11:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Surai held the envelope with the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,typed label.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Everin didn't walk toward me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He stayed in the doorway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,As if he knew that walking would
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,be worse than staying still.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at him over the old
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.05,0:11:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at his surname written
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,in my head in letters that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.34,0:11:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly carried another weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,For three months I'd forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,what that surname was capable of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.64,0:11:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The tape reminded me in four
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.93,0:11:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.02,0:11:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Penthouse had a view of the lake
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,in good silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first time in three
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,months that the silence bothered
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.92,0:11:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I arrived with the tape inside a
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,large envelope, holding it with
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,both hands as if it were heavier
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,than it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.88,0:11:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The paper was slightly crumpled
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,at the edges from how much I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,gripped it in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Everin had come behind me with
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:11:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario in the other vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:11:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't try to talk to me in
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:11:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,When I walked into the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Penthouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,he was already sitting in the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Jacket opened and hands clasped
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,in his lap,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting without hurry, without
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,visible anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He just pointed to the couch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to listen again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I put the tape into the little
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,tape player Dario had managed to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,find somewhere in the last two
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The machine was old, a faded
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,sand color,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,with press buttons that made a
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,satisfying mechanical click when
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,they latched.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I pressed play.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's voice came out again
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,through that tiny speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Slightly muffled, as if it were
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,coming from inside a room that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,had been closed for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,With that strange quality of
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,something recorded carefully so
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,it wouldn't be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everin listened without moving,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,without commenting,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,without crossing his arms or
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.13,0:12:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,looking away or trying to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,protect me from what I already
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When it ended, he stayed silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of silence that isn't
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.66,0:12:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,an absence of an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:12:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.14,0:13:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you want me to say is
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,going to sound like a defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to defend myself
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.06,0:13:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He breathed in deep slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know this tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your surname.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.76,0:13:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He took a while to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked at the floor for a
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,second and then looked at me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,with an expression I was still
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,learning to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.48,0:13:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It was something more honest
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,than both.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the face of a man who
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,grew up without the luxury of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,pretending the world was simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.32,0:13:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That this happened before I
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,existed as a melvani.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And that if you need space, I'll
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked for space.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.12,0:13:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wednesday passed slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I slept in the guest room with
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the window a jar and the sound
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,of the lake arriving in low
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,waves
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that couldn't fill the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The mattress was too firm and
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,smelled faintly of artificial
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.71,0:13:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,lavender,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that hotel scent that was
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,supposed to be comforting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But that night only reminded me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sleeping in a room that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't mine
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:13:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,inside an apartment that still
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,felt like his.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I crossed paths with ever and
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,twice in the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,One of those times his hair was
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,wet and his shirt was open at
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the first button.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And both times he looked away
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,with a politeness that hurt me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,more than if he'd insisted on
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There was something in his care
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that weighed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,As if keeping his distance were
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the greatest effort he'd ever
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,made.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thursday morning, Sarah showed
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,up with coffee and a giant
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.81,0:14:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,croissant wrapped in parchment
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.54,0:14:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Still warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The heat of the bundle passed
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,through my hands when she set it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,on the counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.92,0:14:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And for a moment I just stared
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.96,0:14:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,As if the whole gesture were too
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.38,0:14:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,complicated to receive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought carbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't bring good sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's already a start.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She sat on the kitchen counter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and crossed her arms over the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,ledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,With the posture of someone who
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,was going to stay there as long
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.97,0:14:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,as needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She looked at the TV in the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.16,0:14:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,living room,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,which was on with no sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even know why I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,turned it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd turned it on because the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,silence of the penthouse became
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,a concrete thing inside my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:14:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,if I let it grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the logo of the local
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,gossip radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The one I always pretended not
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to listen to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But the two hosts playing studio
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,in the background and a central
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,microphone they used for
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.50,0:15:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.52,0:15:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,From neighborhood squabbles to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,national scandal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The headline underneath, in
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,yellow capital letters,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,took up half the screen,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,criminal informants daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,organized the gala of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So I pressed the remote and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,turned up the volume.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A piece of the tape played on
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It was short.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe 40 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was exactly the part where my
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,father gave the second name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no context.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.78,0:15:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no story before it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There was none of the part where
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,his voice grew more tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,As if he were choosing his words
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,very carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.64,0:15:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,As if the situation weren't
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just his voice saying a
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,man's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Clean and alone on the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dry as an accusation that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,already arrived with the verdict
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:15:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.90,0:16:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So I didn't answer right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a slight tightening in
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.11,0:16:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,her jaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The sign I knew for contained
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.18,0:16:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm going to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.58,0:16:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I got up and walked to the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,living room window.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The lake was calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A cold gray blue autumn morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,With a few small boats too far
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.31,0:16:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,off to identify.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And a thin mist near the shore
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that made everything slightly
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,imprecise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a photo taken with the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.95,0:16:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,wrong lens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about how many people
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,were listening to that sentence
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,from my father at that exact
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In the coffee line.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.96,0:16:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In the dentist's waiting room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,In the office elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about the hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.42,0:16:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,sponsors hearing it on the way
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to the 10 o'clock meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about the parents of
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,my school classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,People who had known my father
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.54,0:16:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,at neighborhood dinners.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,People who would swear now that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,they'd always suspected
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,something about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They cut everything that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,mattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Those creeps live off this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's diaper journalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dirty it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dirty another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.96,0:16:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a dry, short laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind that comes before
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,crying if I'm not careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So I came to me and squeezed my
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,hand over the counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to get out of here for
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.91,0:17:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.24,0:17:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to the old apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The apartment where I'd lived
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,before the gala.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where I'd made the dumbest
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,decision of my adult life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Eiring an escort because I was
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,afraid of being looked at with
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The apartment was still in my
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't been able to hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.34,0:17:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There was something
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.29,0:17:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,superstitious in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In keeping a piece of myself
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.93,0:17:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,stored in a place where no one
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.39,0:17:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,could reach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I opened the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.64,0:17:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of stale air.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And of an old perfume I no
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,longer wore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Baintly sweet and a little
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,suffocating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,With that added layer of dust
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.23,0:17:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,places gather when they go a
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,long time without breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The furniture was covered with
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,white sheets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And the light coming through the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.03,0:17:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,shutters created stripes on the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,wood floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I walked straight to the hallway
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the bottom drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:17:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And took out my father's box of
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I sat on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There were birthday photos and
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:17:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,vacation photos and Sunday
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,morning photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.74,0:18:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a photo of him
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,carrying me in his arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,On the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,With a floppy straw hat on his
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And his eyes half closed from
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,all the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There was the yellow dress he'd
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,bought me in some small town
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,market.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Holded at the bottom of the box
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,because I'd never been able to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The fabric was slightly faded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,With a permanent crease down the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,center where it had been rolled
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,up for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.94,0:18:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And as I ran my fingers across
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the surface I thought that faded
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,yellow was the most his thing I
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,still had.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And underneath the dress, I
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,found the birthday cassette
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.28,0:18:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd recorded an entire tape
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,from my 12th birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd sung.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Read a piece of a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sent a message to my future self
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,with that ceremonial seriousness
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.48,0:18:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,he put into things he considered
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't listened to the tape a
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,single time in over 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I was afraid his voice would
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,come out different from what I
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.97,0:18:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thenner, stranger,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Deformed by time or by memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a portable tape player
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:18:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Smaller than the palm of my
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:18:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The battery still worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I slotted the tape in carefully
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,as if the plastic were fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,As if the wrong pressure could
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.05,0:19:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,erase what was stored inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I pressed the button.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,His voice came out singing happy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the same voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The same texture.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The same slight rasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The same way of holding the A at
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the end of words as if each
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,syllable needed more room than
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.46,0:19:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the voice from the vault
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the voice of every Sunday
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,morning of my childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.84,0:19:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the breakfast table with the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,big cup that was always his.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the dark hallway when he
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,checked whether I was asleep
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,before turning off the living
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.30,0:19:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,room light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I started to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The way I hadn't cried since the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.25,0:19:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,altar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.10,0:19:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My hand flat on my chest as if I
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,needed to hold something in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I sat on the floor of the empty
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.02,0:19:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,With the stripes of light across
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of stale air all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Listening to my father sing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,happy birthday to me at 12 years
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,old.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And I kept thinking about the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.68,0:19:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,moment he'd had to choose
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.83,0:19:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,between protecting me and
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:19:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,continuing to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,look like a simple man in my
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether he'd hesitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it had been easy or
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.49,0:20:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether he knew in that birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What he'd already done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.82,0:20:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sarai came to get me in the late
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't ask anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.86,0:20:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Which was the most generous
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,gesture she could have offered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I went back to the penthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The lake was already dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The boat lights reflecting on
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the water and crooked trembling
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,lines that dissolved as soon as
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the wind passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I went in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Everin was in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleeve still rolled to his
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.73,0:20:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,elbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.64,0:20:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Making something in a pan that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,he turned off when he heard me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A quiet movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Unhurried.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,As if he'd been waiting for this
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.31,0:20:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,hour without admitting he was
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.51,0:20:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked at me with the kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,look that asks for nothing and
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.21,0:20:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,promises nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It just receives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to sleep in the guest
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,room one more night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.86,0:20:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.46,0:20:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.40,0:20:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I walked down the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped halfway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The wood floor was cold under my
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:20:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,socks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:20:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And the hallway had that late
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,night dimness that made
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,everything a little more honest
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,than during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.10,0:21:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I went back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Everin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for not trying to fix
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.40,0:21:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He lowered his eyes for a
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When he looked at me again,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,there was something different
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.22,0:21:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.76,0:21:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Not hurt, not resignation, but a
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.18,0:21:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of calm, the cost dearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of calm he must have
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,learned the worst way possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.56,0:21:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.48,0:21:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That night, before lying down, I
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.81,0:21:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,went through the hotel lobby to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.54,0:21:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,pick up a folder I'd left in the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,office.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The reception was quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Only one clerk at the desk and
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.32,0:21:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the reduced late night lighting
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that made the marble floor
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.05,0:21:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,warmer than
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.58,0:21:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The neighborhood paper was
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.82,0:21:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,folded on top of the counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.56,0:21:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A small headline.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In the lower corner of the front
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.24,0:21:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,page.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.00,0:21:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvin Harth was going to trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked for two seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't feel anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't feel relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.66,0:21:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't feel anything concrete.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Which was strange after so many
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,months waiting for exactly that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.36,0:21:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,headline.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.44,0:21:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was as if it had turned small
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.17,0:21:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,inside me without my noticing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.73,0:22:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,when.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.26,0:22:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I put the paper back in its
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.60,0:22:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,place and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.36,0:22:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I got back to the penthouse
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,close to 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever and had already laying
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,down, or had the delicacy to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.41,0:22:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,pretend he had.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.14,0:22:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I took off my shoes in the
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.30,0:22:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.30,0:22:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.24,0:22:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wouldn't make noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.74,0:22:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to the guest room.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I laid down with the window a
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.66,0:22:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,jar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.86,0:22:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The cold off the late coming in
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.55,0:22:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and thin waves that barely moved
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.30,0:22:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.44,0:22:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The doorbell rang.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.78,0:22:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at the clock on the
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.93,0:22:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,nightstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.98,0:22:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,11.04.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.44,0:22:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No one showed up at that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.46,0:22:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,penthouse unannounced.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.92,0:22:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario filtered everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.27,0:22:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,including late night visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.50,0:22:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless it was someone Dario
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.70,0:22:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't filter for another
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.91,0:22:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.70,0:22:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I got up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.86,0:22:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I walked to the entrance monitor
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.30,0:22:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a woman standing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.51,0:22:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,downstairs in the camera's
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.72,0:22:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.50,0:22:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark heavy coat, straight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.87,0:22:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.42,0:22:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Grey hair pulled into a low bun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.09,0:22:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,with a firmness that seemed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,deliberate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.68,0:22:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She wasn't looking at the inner
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.97,0:22:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,com or the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.30,0:22:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She was looking straight ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.65,0:22:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,with the specific patience of
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.95,0:22:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,someone who knows she's going to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.39,0:22:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.48,0:22:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,let in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.84,0:23:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,When she lifted her eyes to the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.39,0:23:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,monitor, I recognized her
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.63,0:23:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,without ever having seen her
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.03,0:23:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,before.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.76,0:23:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They were black firm eyes that I
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.21,0:23:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,knew from every morning of the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,last three months on someone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.84,0:23:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,else's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.06,0:23:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I pressed the inner com with a
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.31,0:23:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,trembling hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.50,0:23:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.28,0:23:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Her voice came weighted with a
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.61,0:23:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,light Italian accent.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.22,0:23:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Precise without affectation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.52,0:23:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.70,0:23:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Bruno Melvani.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.04,0:23:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to tell you something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.23,0:23:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,about your father before my son
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.55,0:23:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,finds out on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.86,0:23:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Doorbell buzzed again, and the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,sound pushed me toward the door
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.12,0:23:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,before I decided to open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.84,0:23:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was already in the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.90,0:23:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.88,0:23:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Barefoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.64,0:23:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Black shirt wrinkled like a man
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.05,0:23:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,who hadn't slept.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.46,0:23:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyes met mine for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.46,0:23:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A long second.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.76,0:23:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Waded with a question neither of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.22,0:23:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,us put into words.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.56,0:23:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't ask who it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.38,0:23:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he already knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.40,0:23:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I opened the penthouse door, and
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.15,0:23:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the woman waiting on the other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.79,0:23:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,side took off her coat with
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.26,0:23:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the delicacy of someone entering
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.70,0:23:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,a home for the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.83,0:23:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,without being sure she'd be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.04,0:23:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.96,0:23:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,60 something.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.36,0:24:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Gray hair pulled into a low bun.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.52,0:24:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Discrete lipstick invaded wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.74,0:24:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A thin chain of old gold resting
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.35,0:24:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,on the skin of her chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.96,0:24:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The Italian accent appeared in
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.37,0:24:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the first word.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.64,0:24:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Light like the smoke still
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.78,0:24:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,rising from the kitchen coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.66,0:24:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The one I'd forgotten to turn
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.96,0:24:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,off.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.48,0:24:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,May I come in, Noelia?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.06,0:24:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She knew my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.98,0:24:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She knew enough to wait until 11
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.58,0:24:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,at night at the entrance of a
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.04,0:24:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,building that wasn't hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.76,0:24:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,With late cold outside and a
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.10,0:24:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,discretion that told me more
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.45,0:24:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,than any introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.16,0:24:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You may.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.08,0:24:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.18,0:24:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And step to side.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.66,0:24:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever and approach to his mother
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.90,0:24:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.10,0:24:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Without touching her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.42,0:24:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The two exchanged a short, dry
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.44,0:24:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,look.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.20,0:24:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And I realized that between them
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.05,0:24:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.60,0:24:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There were old silences.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.34,0:24:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind carried for decades
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.85,0:24:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,without needing words.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.58,0:24:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the words wouldn't ease
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.98,0:24:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,anything anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.70,0:24:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Bruno Melvani set her purse on
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.39,0:24:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the coffee table carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.56,0:24:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,As if the gesture mattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.28,0:24:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And looked at me with a calm
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.48,0:24:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that hurt more than any hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.22,0:24:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I came before he found out on
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.88,0:24:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.58,0:24:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She said.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.64,0:25:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tilting her head toward her son.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.60,0:25:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There are things about your
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.03,0:25:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,father that I had to keep for
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.56,0:25:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,more than 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.84,0:25:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And that are now coming out of a
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.48,0:25:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,vault I believed no longer
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.81,0:25:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.36,0:25:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt my stomach tightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.94,0:25:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Bruno sat on the couch.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.16,0:25:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Smooth her dark skirt over her
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.23,0:25:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.36,0:25:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And waited for me to sit too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.82,0:25:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The apartment was quiet except
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.22,0:25:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,for the low wind at the windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.74,0:25:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever in stayed standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.62,0:25:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaning against the kitchen
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.67,0:25:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.68,0:25:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Two steps behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.94,0:25:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.96,0:25:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In that house, that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.20,0:25:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The voice belonged to his
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.20,0:25:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.02,0:25:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And Taro Cross came to my
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.55,0:25:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,husband 22 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.20,0:25:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Bruno began slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.80,0:25:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Choosing each word like someone
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.27,0:25:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,crossing thin ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.12,0:25:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to sell anyone out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.34,0:25:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,To infiltrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.58,0:25:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a dissident faction
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.95,0:25:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that had started threatening
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.27,0:25:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,entire families by name.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.86,0:25:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother and you were on a
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.13,0:25:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,list that reached your father's
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.49,0:25:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,hands from inside a department
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.81,0:25:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,he
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.90,0:25:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,coordinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.78,0:25:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He had two choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.34,0:25:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Get you out of the country and
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.00,0:25:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,lose you another way or agree to
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.77,0:26:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.48,0:26:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The coffee cup on the coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.85,0:26:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,table stopped existing for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.62,0:26:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard Bruno's breathing louder
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.10,0:26:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,than any sound coming from the
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.49,0:26:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,building or the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.96,0:26:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.22,0:26:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She went on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.90,0:26:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He arranged a staged handover
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.47,0:26:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,with the old Melvani.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.24,0:26:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And Taro would give three names
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.71,0:26:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that were already technically
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.08,0:26:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.66,0:26:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,From the standpoint of the
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.73,0:26:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,family's accounting.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.22,0:26:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And in exchange the dissidents
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.61,0:26:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,would believe he was with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.28,0:26:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a long game.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.80,0:26:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan was to expose
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.86,0:26:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,everything in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.30,0:26:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,With names and dates and faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.64,0:26:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The old Melvani knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.30,0:26:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.26,0:26:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,For years, it was the most
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.96,0:26:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,expensive secret of my marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.54,0:26:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The three men who died.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.28,0:26:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My voice came out almost
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.46,0:26:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,breathless.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.00,0:26:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They died because someone from
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.70,0:26:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,inside our family sold the plan
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.45,0:26:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,ahead of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.56,0:26:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't your father's tape
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.88,0:26:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that killed those men.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.32,0:26:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was internal betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.36,0:26:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,On Taro found out who had sold
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.84,0:26:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.62,0:26:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He was going to expose it in
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.93,0:26:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,both directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.32,0:26:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,To the dissidents to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.26,0:26:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He was killed before he could.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.26,0:26:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I lifted my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.70,0:26:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She waited.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.68,0:27:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I needed to hear the name from
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.11,0:27:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,her mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.02,0:27:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And she knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.20,0:27:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,New it the same way you know
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.46,0:27:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,when someone is holding a door
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.82,0:27:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.54,0:27:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiting for someone on the other
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.39,0:27:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,side to push.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.86,0:27:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Massimo Grell.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.04,0:27:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Bruno said.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.08,0:27:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Massimo who killed your
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.39,0:27:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,father.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.18,0:27:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And my husband died in the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.44,0:27:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,ambush that followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.00,0:27:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely because Massimo passed
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.39,0:27:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,our movements to the dissidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.32,0:27:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In one week, he had the two
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.76,0:27:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,widows he needed to control what
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.46,0:27:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,was left.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.54,0:27:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.46,0:27:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the sound of ever in
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.68,0:27:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,breathing slowly through his
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.90,0:27:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.62,0:27:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Like someone holding an entire
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.10,0:27:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,wave inside his chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.58,0:27:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So as not to knock the room
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.96,0:27:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,down.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.62,0:27:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you never tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.90,0:27:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.22,0:27:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Because as long as Massimo
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.72,0:27:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,thought I didn't know, he kept
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.44,0:27:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.44,0:27:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bruno answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.58,0:27:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Without looking away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.20,0:27:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And as long as Everin believed
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.78,0:27:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,in the father figure Massimo
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.25,0:27:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,built over two decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.22,0:27:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Massimo wouldn't need to kill my
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.93,0:27:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,son too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.62,0:27:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at Everin.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.92,0:27:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He was still.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.14,0:27:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand closed over the stone
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.41,0:27:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.34,0:27:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,His knuckles white against the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.71,0:27:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,dark granite.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.72,0:27:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He said nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.00,0:28:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He only tilted his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.72,0:28:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.56,0:28:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Like someone recognizing a pain
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.86,0:28:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that had already been inside him
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.21,0:28:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.66,0:28:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiting to be named by someone
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.54,0:28:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,who survived to name it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.26,0:28:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Bruno stood up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.50,0:28:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She ran her hand across my face
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.97,0:28:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,with a lightness that didn't ask
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.50,0:28:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.54,0:28:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And even so.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.70,0:28:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't invade anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.28,0:28:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the gesture of a woman
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.67,0:28:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,who had learned the difference
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.11,0:28:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,between consoling and invading.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.16,0:28:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father died protecting you,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.65,0:28:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Noelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.66,0:28:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The old vault held the wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.07,0:28:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.88,0:28:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere, there's a complete
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.52,0:28:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.22,0:28:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The one where he explains
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.27,0:28:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,everything in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.52,0:28:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,With the plan, the names, and
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.27,0:28:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.74,0:28:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Massimo spent 22 years looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.28,0:28:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If he learns that the tape from
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.53,0:28:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the envelope reached the hotel,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.26,0:28:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll come after the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.72,0:28:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And he'll come after me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.48,0:28:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She picked up the purse from the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.72,0:28:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,center of the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.00,0:28:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Everin finally moved to walk her
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.69,0:28:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.72,0:28:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,His mother placed an open hand
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.25,0:28:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,on her son's chest for two
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.57,0:28:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.54,0:28:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just two.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.66,0:28:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Like someone touching a wall to
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.99,0:28:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,feel whether it's still
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.97,0:28:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.00,0:28:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether the material still
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.27,0:28:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,holds.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.08,0:29:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going home tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.84,0:29:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She said to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.82,0:29:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Her voice low and firm without
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.69,0:29:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.64,0:29:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get a room far from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.44,0:29:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No one needs to know where.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.10,0:29:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The door closed behind her.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.72,0:29:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound of the latch was the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.94,0:29:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,only noise in the whole
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.87,0:29:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.84,0:29:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I stayed sitting on the couch.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.74,0:29:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in state in the same place,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.54,0:29:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,leaning against the counter
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.62,0:29:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,without turning around.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.38,0:29:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to the kitchen when she
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.79,0:29:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,left.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.38,0:29:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't fleeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.86,0:29:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the only wall in the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.16,0:29:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,house where I could stay
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.32,0:29:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,standing without looking at
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.62,0:29:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Noelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.56,0:29:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,While my world finished falling
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.32,0:29:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in orderly silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.40,0:29:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace by peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.58,0:29:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a structure collapsing from
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.27,0:29:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the inside out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.46,0:29:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I turned on the faucet just for
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.08,0:29:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.06,0:29:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I braised both hands on the cold
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.23,0:29:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,stone counter and closed my
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.06,0:29:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.84,0:29:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The first thing that came wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.74,0:29:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Massimo.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.72,0:29:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It was her.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.00,0:29:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Backstage at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.72,0:29:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Three months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.96,0:29:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The hallway smelled of expensive
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.80,0:29:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,flowers and a electrical cable
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.52,0:29:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,heated by the spotlights to set
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.42,0:29:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,up crew head left on.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.92,0:29:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd come in through the service
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.48,0:29:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,door as arranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.34,0:30:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The false name on the tip of my
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.54,0:30:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.62,0:30:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The crest ring in the inner
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.95,0:30:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,pocket of my jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.56,0:30:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Away from my right hand for the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.29,0:30:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,first time in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.72,0:30:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She appeared at the end of the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.14,0:30:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,hallway with a clipboard pressed
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.66,0:30:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,against her chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.92,0:30:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And a wet charcoal colored
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.38,0:30:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.86,0:30:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Her hair still damp from rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.86,0:30:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Her mouth tense like someone
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.38,0:30:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,who'd spent hours holding in a
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.02,0:30:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.90,0:30:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She looked at me as if she were
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.29,0:30:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,checking a catering order.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.94,0:30:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I scanned the three exits before
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.68,0:30:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed the way she breathed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.36,0:30:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Scanning exits was muscle
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.03,0:30:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.90,0:30:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Noticing the way she breathed
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.43,0:30:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,was the first thing I'd done
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.91,0:30:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,without deciding to in a long
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.44,0:30:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.06,0:30:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered the ballroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.84,0:30:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment the exfiance
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.25,0:30:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,approached with a rehearsed line
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.22,0:30:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and she answered with sarcasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.40,0:30:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I even had to open my
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.82,0:30:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.62,0:30:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.64,0:30:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It was exactly there that
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.85,0:30:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,something happened that I didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.39,0:30:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,have a name for in my
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.41,0:30:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,vocabulary.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.82,0:30:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd walked into that gala to
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.25,0:30:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,identify a traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.80,0:30:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And in four seconds a woman I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.51,0:30:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,never seen in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.72,0:30:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Had parried a public humiliation
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.57,0:31:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,with the serenity of someone who
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.42,0:31:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,had nothing left to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.32,0:31:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And still chose to defend
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.69,0:31:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,herself with elegance.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.42,0:31:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew how to identify courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.54,0:31:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It had been my trade since I was
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.37,0:31:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,22.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.20,0:31:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This was something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.70,0:31:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This was a woman who laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.13,0:31:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,when she was about to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.96,0:31:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And I recognized the texture of
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.75,0:31:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,that laugh before I even knew
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.43,0:31:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,her full name.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.68,0:31:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The service hallway came next,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.63,0:31:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,out of chronological order.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.92,0:31:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The side door.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.96,0:31:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of flowers and of
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.66,0:31:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,invisible work mixing in the air
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.67,0:31:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,between the white walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.66,0:31:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she didn't know who I
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.35,0:31:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,was.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.04,0:31:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I answered that she was the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.42,0:31:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,first person in a long time I
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.89,0:31:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't want to manipulate.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.98,0:31:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.00,0:31:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't predicted it would be
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.69,0:31:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,true when I opened my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.78,0:31:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the truth wasn't usually
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.55,0:31:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,my starting point in any
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.88,0:31:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.24,0:31:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My fingers moved toward her face
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.06,0:31:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,a millimeter before her chin
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.66,0:31:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.38,0:31:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.54,0:31:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.22,0:31:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first time in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.22,0:31:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped out of respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.20,0:31:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Not calculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.68,0:31:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the big screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.32,0:32:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My face on national broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.06,0:32:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The ballroom that froze in a
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.55,0:32:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,second.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.44,0:32:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The rivals coming in through the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.18,0:32:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,side doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.24,0:32:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have left through the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.42,0:32:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.04,0:32:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd had two roots mapped since
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.49,0:32:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,arriving.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.24,0:32:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.42,0:32:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was always the rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.10,0:32:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The first instruction of any
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.61,0:32:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,family head was to preserve your
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.33,0:32:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,own head above all else.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.06,0:32:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at her across the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.29,0:32:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,ballroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.72,0:32:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She looked back at me with
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.45,0:32:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,disgust, with fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.22,0:32:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,with the remnant of an anger
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.67,0:32:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that hadn't yet crashed down on
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.28,0:32:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.62,0:32:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And she stayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.94,0:32:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.22,0:32:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She stayed with her feet planted
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.74,0:32:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,on the marble of the ballroom
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.12,0:32:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,she herself had organized.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.96,0:32:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I stayed because she had stayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.08,0:32:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first time in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.85,0:32:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I understood why my father used
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.56,0:32:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to say that silence was power.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.70,0:32:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And that power was the only
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.22,0:32:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,thing worth less than standing
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.90,0:32:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,beside the person you choose to
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.64,0:32:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,stand with.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.26,0:32:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I opened my eyes over the sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.74,0:32:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The water was still running.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.58,0:32:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Cold now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.60,0:32:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was when the other
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.00,0:32:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,memory came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.36,0:32:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The one from the morning after
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.87,0:32:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the gala.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.80,0:33:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The car pulling out of the
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.11,0:33:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,hotel's basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.50,0:33:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The engine low.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.24,0:33:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Chicago's streets still wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.18,0:33:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Massimo in the back seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.76,0:33:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Paternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.74,0:33:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,His shoulders relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.42,0:33:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Smiling with that tenderness of
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.00,0:33:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,someone who had raised me after
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.58,0:33:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,my father's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.76,0:33:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He said in Italian,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.70,0:33:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You deserve it, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.88,0:33:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,With the calm of someone who
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.30,0:33:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,believes every word he chooses.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.48,0:33:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I smiled back that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.36,0:33:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I squeezed his shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.12,0:33:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.46,0:33:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,22 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.06,0:33:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Massimo had been at my side in
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.61,0:33:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,every important decision I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.05,0:33:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,made as head of the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.98,0:33:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Including the one that led me to
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.59,0:33:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,pretend to be an escort to
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.90,0:33:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,identify a traitor,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.10,0:33:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,laundering money through the
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.38,0:33:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,event.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.02,0:33:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who had convinced me,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.66,0:33:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,with soft words and a father's
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.35,0:33:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,patience,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.86,0:33:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that the traitor was inside the
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.74,0:33:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,hotel and not inside my own
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.38,0:33:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,office.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.34,0:33:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Had been Massimo.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.70,0:33:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I shut off the faucet.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.40,0:33:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The sentence in the car weighed
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.16,0:33:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,three times as much now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.88,0:33:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You deserve it, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.38,0:33:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, deserve, because he
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.10,0:33:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,knew exactly what I didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.70,0:34:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,deserve to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.84,0:34:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.30,0:34:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because 22 years earlier, he'd
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.80,0:34:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,killed the man who was trying to
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.39,0:34:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,give two women back their own
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.84,0:34:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,names.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.52,0:34:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I breathed in deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.22,0:34:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Once.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.14,0:34:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.14,0:34:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Through my nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.98,0:34:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all I could allow myself
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.88,0:34:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,without breaking something.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.90,0:34:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When Evern came back from the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.49,0:34:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,kitchen, he didn't try to touch
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.20,0:34:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.58,0:34:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He sat at the other end of the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.11,0:34:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,couch, with a meter of space
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.54,0:34:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,between us that neither of us
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.02,0:34:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,had the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.38,0:34:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,energy to cross, and stayed
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.79,0:34:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at the floor with his
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.31,0:34:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,elbows on his knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.80,0:34:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.02,0:34:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, before he tried
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.36,0:34:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.44,0:34:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He nodded without lifting his
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.69,0:34:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,head.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.26,0:34:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to leave here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.48,0:34:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I added, because it was
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.55,0:34:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,important to say it out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.34,0:34:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,To breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.48,0:34:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.30,0:34:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He said.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.74,0:34:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Low.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.00,0:34:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The house is yours, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.62,0:34:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The house wasn't mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.04,0:34:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The house belonged to a surname
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.38,0:34:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that had killed my father,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.96,0:34:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,through a man who still walked
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.33,0:34:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,free.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.12,0:34:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Paternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.14,0:34:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sitting at meeting tables with
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.53,0:34:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Evern on Tuesday mornings,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.32,0:34:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,probably with coffee and
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.43,0:34:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.34,0:34:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But at that moment, I didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.64,0:34:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,have the strength to correct the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.12,0:34:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.04,0:35:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the rest of my father's
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.40,0:35:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,tape somewhere in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.22,0:35:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A Malvani mother who had agreed
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.78,0:35:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to sleep far from her own home
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.30,0:35:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,out of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.90,0:35:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And the name Masimo Grell,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.37,0:35:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,pulsing behind my eyes like a
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.00,0:35:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,light that wouldn't turn off
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.58,0:35:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,no.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.22,0:35:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Matter how much I tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.12,0:35:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I got up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.24,0:35:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I walked to the guest room.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.88,0:35:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped in the doorway, hand
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.52,0:35:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,on the frame and looked back.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.56,0:35:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Evern was in the same position
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.94,0:35:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,on the couch.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.04,0:35:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The shoulders lowered for the
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.42,0:35:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,first time in three months of
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.80,0:35:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,penthouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.54,0:35:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and shared dinners and silences
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.90,0:35:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that were good because they were
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.29,0:35:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.12,0:35:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the lowered shoulders
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.28,0:35:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,weren't rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.26,0:35:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They were the weight of an
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.49,0:35:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,inheritance he hadn't asked for,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.00,0:35:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and that someone had spent
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.28,0:35:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,decades building on his
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.42,0:35:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulders
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.86,0:35:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,without him knowing the real
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.85,0:35:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,price.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.92,0:35:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Masimo, I said out loud,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.16,0:35:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,because the first time needed to
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.68,0:35:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,be between the two of us before
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.15,0:35:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.34,0:35:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Masimo, he repeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.38,0:35:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,with the same voice of someone
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.80,0:35:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,confirming a sentence he already
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.32,0:35:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,knew was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.50,0:35:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was at that instant that his
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.00,0:35:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,phone rang on the coffee table.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.92,0:35:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We both looked at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.96,0:36:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,an involuntary reflex,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.82,0:36:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,as if the whole apartment had
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.07,0:36:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,held its breath together.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.14,0:36:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The screen lit up with the cold
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.77,0:36:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,late night light.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.02,0:36:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The name rose in clear letters
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.42,0:36:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,on the display,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.62,0:36:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,as if it were a joke no one in
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.82,0:36:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the room had authorized.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.42,0:36:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Masimo, Evern looked at me,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.72,0:36:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.90,0:36:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He answered without bringing the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.21,0:36:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,phone to his face,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.28,0:36:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,on speaker, his thumb firm and
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.88,0:36:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,motionless on the coffee table.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.02,0:36:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The voice came sweet, slow,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.54,0:36:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,an Italian first and then in
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.02,0:36:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,English,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.96,0:36:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,with that precise tenderness of
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.54,0:36:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,someone calling to ask whether
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.07,0:36:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,his son had slept well,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.68,0:36:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and whether he'd eaten anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.94,0:36:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Evern,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.30,0:36:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,figlio mio,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.56,0:36:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,your mother didn't come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.30,0:36:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I got worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.50,0:36:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you happen to know where
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.85,0:36:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.44,0:36:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The cemetery that Monday morning
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.89,0:36:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,was nearly empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.06,0:36:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky had that washed out
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.45,0:36:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,light of late spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.06,0:36:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind that looks faded but
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.53,0:36:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,burns your eyes if you look too
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.11,0:36:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,long.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.80,0:36:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And the wind came off the lake
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.30,0:36:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,with the smell of still water
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.75,0:36:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and damp grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.72,0:36:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I walked alone down the side
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.28,0:36:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,lane,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.90,0:37:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,with a small bouquet of white
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.31,0:37:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,daisies in my hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.60,0:37:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,because daisies were what my
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.76,0:37:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,father always bought when he
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.93,0:37:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,came home from work,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.76,0:37:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,with the excuse that he didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.40,0:37:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,have money for roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.06,0:37:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd arrive home with the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.09,0:37:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,flowers a little crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.62,0:37:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The stems still slick with
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.87,0:37:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,water,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.68,0:37:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and put them in the jar by the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.92,0:37:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,kitchen sink as if that were
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.07,0:37:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,enough for the whole week.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.46,0:37:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It always was.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.80,0:37:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,His headstone was clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.46,0:37:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I came twice a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.92,0:37:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Always quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.98,0:37:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Always without saying much.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.50,0:37:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That morning, I crouched and
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.03,0:37:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,took more time arranging the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.56,0:37:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,flowers than I needed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.30,0:37:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Separating the stems one by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.50,0:37:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,straightening what was already
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.65,0:37:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.50,0:37:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My hands needed something to do
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.91,0:37:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,while I gathered
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.64,0:37:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the words.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.90,0:37:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.36,0:37:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My voice came out low.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.86,0:37:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Without theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.14,0:37:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no one nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.72,0:37:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I could cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.86,0:37:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It took me a few seconds to
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.30,0:37:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,realize I wasn't going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.98,0:37:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,For 22 years I called you the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.61,0:37:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,man who left us early.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.22,0:37:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,For 22 years, I put on your
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.89,0:37:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,account the bill's mom paid
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.57,0:37:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.40,0:37:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,For 22 years, I explained you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.51,0:37:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,from a distance to others,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.92,0:38:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,as if you'd had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.68,0:38:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran my thumb over the letter C
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.22,0:38:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,of the surname and graved in the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.75,0:38:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.04,0:38:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The surface was cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.16,0:38:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in the morning sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.78,0:38:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You had a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.24,0:38:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You chose us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.56,0:38:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I only found out too late to
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.98,0:38:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you the way I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.80,0:38:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I stayed crouched another
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.10,0:38:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.90,0:38:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind stirred the daisies.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.80,0:38:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The anger when it came was small
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.13,0:38:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.32,0:38:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Without smudges, it wasn't at
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.20,0:38:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.80,0:38:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It was at the man who had
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.48,0:38:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,decided for both of them
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.10,0:38:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,silently for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.00,0:38:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Using the name of a father that
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.44,0:38:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't his to protect a power
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.78,0:38:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that should never have existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.22,0:38:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.50,0:38:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I don't know how yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.04,0:38:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.10,0:38:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I stood up.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.14,0:38:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind passed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.58,0:38:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I wiped my hands on my pants and
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.20,0:38:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,walked down the lane toward the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.77,0:38:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,gate without looking back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.44,0:38:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario was waiting for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.65,0:38:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,leaning against the black car at
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.20,0:38:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the bend in the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.78,0:38:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,With the posture of someone
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.01,0:38:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,who'd learned to take up the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.29,0:38:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,least space possible in any
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.53,0:38:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.58,0:38:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark suit even in early spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.72,0:38:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sun glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.94,0:39:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,His tie loosened exactly one
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.33,0:39:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,millimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.88,0:39:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Which for him probably counted
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.60,0:39:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,as a concession to the season.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.72,0:39:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sarai was in the passenger seat
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.17,0:39:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,of her car.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.10,0:39:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind his.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.24,0:39:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,With the window open.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.68,0:39:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Enter hair pinned in a careless
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.42,0:39:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,twist.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.26,0:39:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Reading something on her phone
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.51,0:39:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,with the expression of someone
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.76,0:39:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,pretending not to be paying
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.89,0:39:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,attention
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.26,0:39:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to absolutely everything around
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.19,0:39:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.46,0:39:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't expecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.02,0:39:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.96,0:39:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.02,0:39:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.20,0:39:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In his usual half voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.96,0:39:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Controlled and without
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.79,0:39:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,inflection.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.88,0:39:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured it'd be simpler for me
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.35,0:39:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to bring it than to send it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.64,0:39:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He opened the trunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.12,0:39:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He took out a sealed cardboard
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.58,0:39:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,box.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.18,0:39:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Medium sized.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.40,0:39:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No label.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.52,0:39:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Packing tape run three times
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.88,0:39:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,around the edges as if the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.14,0:39:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,contents demanded extra care.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.86,0:39:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It weighed enough that both his
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.21,0:39:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,arms compensated for the weight
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.55,0:39:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,for an instant before adjusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.62,0:39:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.08,0:39:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He said.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.04,0:39:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything he has.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.66,0:39:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.08,0:39:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,At Dario.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.18,0:39:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,At the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.30,0:39:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Which still had that washed out
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.61,0:39:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,light that chose nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.12,0:39:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he send a note?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.16,0:39:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario took from the inner pocket
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.87,0:40:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,of his jacket a folded card.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.94,0:40:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And handed it to me without
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.05,0:40:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.14,0:40:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Evern's handwriting was
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.09,0:40:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.96,0:40:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.86,0:40:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Without flourish.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.20,0:40:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The capital letters a bit larger
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.64,0:40:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,than necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.86,0:40:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,As if they were holding
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.87,0:40:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,something behind them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.02,0:40:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.22,0:40:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.36,0:40:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I put the card in my coat
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.58,0:40:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.40,0:40:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Close to my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.78,0:40:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Surai got out of the car with
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.25,0:40:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,two cups of coffee and handed me
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.88,0:40:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.50,0:40:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at me for a second with
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.85,0:40:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that silence she used when she
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.15,0:40:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't want me to know she was
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.46,0:40:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.78,0:40:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Her glance passed quickly over
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.41,0:40:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario before returning to him
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.99,0:40:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,with the speed of someone who
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.57,0:40:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,tried not to
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.22,0:40:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,look and hadn't managed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.44,0:40:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.48,0:40:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Surai said.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.60,0:40:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,With a slanted smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.24,0:40:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,In the middle of a Chicago
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.72,0:40:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.64,0:40:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Who introduced you to summer
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.86,0:40:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,around here creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.52,0:40:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario turned his face slightly
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.98,0:40:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,toward her.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.72,0:40:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The dark glasses didn't let his
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.10,0:40:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes show.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.98,0:40:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But the pause before his answer
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.32,0:40:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,was long enough to be
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.22,0:40:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,intentional.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.38,0:40:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you feel hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.86,0:40:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Surai pressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.00,0:40:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Amused by her own advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.32,0:40:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you always ask questions
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.90,0:40:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,about other people's clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.24,0:40:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario shot back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.60,0:41:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Voice dry as paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.36,0:41:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Surai laughed before the end of
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.76,0:41:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,her own answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.94,0:41:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of laugh that doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.15,0:41:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,wait for permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.68,0:41:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.56,0:41:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She said.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.54,0:41:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my way of keeping my sanity
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.03,0:41:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,in the middle of all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.62,0:41:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They I'd each other for a second
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.95,0:41:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,longer than necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.44,0:41:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the only thing in that
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.83,0:41:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,whole morning that pulled a
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.13,0:41:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,smile out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.34,0:41:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Surai took the box from Dario's
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.89,0:41:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,hands without asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.94,0:41:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,As if the weight were an offense
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.67,0:41:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,she resolved before he could try
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.40,0:41:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to carry it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.74,0:41:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Said it in the trunk of our car.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.64,0:41:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And slammed the lid with the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.82,0:41:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,palm of her hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.06,0:41:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.02,0:41:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She said to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.34,0:41:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignoring Dario with the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.39,0:41:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,precision of someone very aware
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.81,0:41:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,of his presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.08,0:41:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a hotel office waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.58,0:41:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.26,0:41:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario nodded to me slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.12,0:41:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.14,0:41:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He got into his own car.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.78,0:41:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,With the same contained gesture
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.52,0:41:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.46,0:41:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had to look the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.12,0:41:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So I wouldn't smile again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.36,0:41:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The hotel's events office
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.95,0:41:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,smelled of warm paper and old
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.79,0:41:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.90,0:41:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The residual scent of two
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.45,0:41:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,arrangements I hadn't had
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.99,0:41:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,changed the week before.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.78,0:41:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the same room where I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.12,0:41:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,kept for months.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.32,0:42:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The folder with the evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.44,0:42:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,against Calvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.68,0:42:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The same dark wood shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.46,0:42:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The same lamp with the
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.51,0:42:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,butter-colored shade that had
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.90,0:42:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,needed a stronger bulb for at
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.29,0:42:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,least two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.38,0:42:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The same door with the lock that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.78,0:42:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,required a shove of the shoulder
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.17,0:42:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to close properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.50,0:42:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I set Evron's box on top of the
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.20,0:42:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.48,0:42:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The same gesture as before,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.31,0:42:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,countless times with Calvin's
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.27,0:42:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,folder.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.36,0:42:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The different weight, the
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.51,0:42:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,completely different feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.50,0:42:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I opened it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.66,0:42:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside, organized into
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.86,0:42:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,subfolders numbered in Evron's
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.49,0:42:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,handwriting on the labels.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.38,0:42:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the entire empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.22,0:42:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Casino contracts with coded
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.76,0:42:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,clauses,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.76,0:42:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,laundering schemes that ran
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.89,0:42:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,through charity events.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.42,0:42:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,At least four of them at hotels
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.88,0:42:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew by name.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.08,0:42:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Names of council members, of two
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.30,0:42:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,mayors, of a retired federal
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.24,0:42:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,judge,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.66,0:42:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,lists of monthly payments with
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.42,0:42:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,dates and initials beside each
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.19,0:42:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.28,0:42:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,meticulous as clean bookkeeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.30,0:42:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,As if Evron had spent the last
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.59,0:42:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,months building.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.06,0:42:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In silence and without telling
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.39,0:42:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.54,0:42:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The very dossier against
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.04,0:42:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.92,0:42:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In a subfolder at the back,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.52,0:43:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,separated from the others by a
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.29,0:43:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,blue tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.36,0:43:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Three thin envelopes with the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.92,0:43:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,label and tarot cross written by
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.63,0:43:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.46,0:43:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Original documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.06,0:43:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Copies of internal reports from
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.66,0:43:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.62,0:43:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The complete transcription of a
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.06,0:43:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,third witnesses testimony
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.22,0:43:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.84,0:43:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Point by point.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.16,0:43:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What Bruna had said the night
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.42,0:43:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,before.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.32,0:43:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I stayed looking at the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.37,0:43:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,envelopes longer than I expected
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.83,0:43:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to need.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.62,0:43:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I held in my hands enough to
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.93,0:43:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,clear my father's name before
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.28,0:43:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,any camera in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.04,0:43:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And enough to send Evron to
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.45,0:43:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,prison for the next 20 odd
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.81,0:43:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,years.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.60,0:43:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I sat in the chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.14,0:43:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Surai sat on the edge of the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.53,0:43:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,desk at my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.60,0:43:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Without joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.84,0:43:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Without filling the silence with
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.20,0:43:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.92,0:43:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She stayed there while I leaped
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.52,0:43:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,through each subfolder.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.02,0:43:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.02,0:43:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Reading enough to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.19,0:43:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,what I was holding
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.94,0:43:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,without needing to read it all
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.30,0:43:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to know the weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.66,0:43:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to decide today.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.62,0:43:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Surai said.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.66,0:43:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,After a long while.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.06,0:43:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.86,0:43:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're going to decide
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.14,0:43:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,today.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.90,0:43:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.82,0:43:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She put her hand over mine for
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.21,0:43:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,two seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.36,0:43:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a third.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.54,0:43:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Which would have been too much
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.83,0:43:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,for both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.80,0:44:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've known you since you were
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.16,0:44:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,22.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.72,0:44:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.10,0:44:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't decide anything in an
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.63,0:44:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,office.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.48,0:44:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You decide over coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.12,0:44:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That was why I ended up inside
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.62,0:44:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the cafe in the hotel's
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.76,0:44:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,neighborhood and hour later.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.16,0:44:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,With the box closed again under
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.87,0:44:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the table and the smell of
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.31,0:44:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,espresso and cinnamon mixed with
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.08,0:44:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the low sound of music no one
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.73,0:44:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,was really listening to.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.42,0:44:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The view in the mirror behind
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.68,0:44:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the counter gave me back my face
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.06,0:44:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,without makeup for the first
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.28,0:44:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,time in
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.58,0:44:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.44,0:44:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at the reflection.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.18,0:44:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The reflection looked back at me
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.83,0:44:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,with the same absent calm of
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.28,0:44:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,someone who's already
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.36,0:44:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,decided and hasn't yet told her
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.05,0:44:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,own body.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.06,0:44:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no longer the woman
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.29,0:44:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,from the altar.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.38,0:44:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no longer the radio
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.66,0:44:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,headline.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.66,0:44:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There was just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.18,0:44:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Over a cup of black coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.90,0:44:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Deciding the rest of my own
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.37,0:44:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,story with my hands wrapped
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.83,0:44:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,around the warm cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.42,0:44:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.88,0:44:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about everin.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.34,0:44:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.96,0:44:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In the exact order the things
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.44,0:44:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,needed to be thought about.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.18,0:44:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I stood up.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.34,0:44:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I went back to the penthouse in
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.97,0:44:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the late afternoon with the box
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.60,0:44:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,again in the passenger seat
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.02,0:44:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and the sun going down over the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.80,0:45:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,lake in tones of old copper.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.40,0:45:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of light that makes
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.83,0:45:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,everything more beautiful and
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.32,0:45:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,heavier at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.16,0:45:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I rode up in the private
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.54,0:45:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,elevator in silence with my own
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.33,0:45:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,reflection accompanying me in
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.01,0:45:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.18,0:45:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,mirrored elevator door until the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.82,0:45:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,floor closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.38,0:45:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I opened the door with the key
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.82,0:45:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd given me three months
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.07,0:45:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.34,0:45:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I've ran with standing in the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.45,0:45:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,living room facing the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.20,0:45:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,phone in his lowered hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.86,0:45:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He hadn't heard the door when he
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.45,0:45:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,turned.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.32,0:45:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyes were different.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.94,0:45:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,With a stillness that wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.45,0:45:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.18,0:45:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the kind of stillness of
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.59,0:45:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,someone who had just received
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.91,0:45:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,news they'd waited their
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.00,0:45:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,whole life for, without knowing
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.64,0:45:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,they were waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.18,0:45:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Massimo, he said simply, as if
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.99,0:45:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the name weighed enough not to
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.79,0:45:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,need anything else around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.72,0:45:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He took my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.00,0:45:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped in the middle of the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.25,0:45:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,room.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.98,0:45:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,When, 40 minutes ago, he called
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.51,0:45:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.52,0:45:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He once the box burned in 24
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.30,0:45:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.14,0:45:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Filmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.96,0:45:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange for my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.62,0:45:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I set the box on the coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.99,0:45:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,table.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.90,0:45:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Between the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.30,0:45:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound of the wood receiving
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.85,0:46:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the weight filled the room for
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.34,0:46:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,one full second.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.14,0:46:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Clean and definitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.64,0:46:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever end looked at the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.14,0:46:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.26,0:46:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He said nothing for a while I
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.61,0:46:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't try to shorten.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.20,0:46:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I sat on the couch.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.74,0:46:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He sat in the armchair across
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.34,0:46:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.00,0:46:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The box between us like a third
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.72,0:46:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,body neither of us invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.82,0:46:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.40,0:46:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Present and motionless.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.98,0:46:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Demanding an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.44,0:46:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The silence lasted three
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.57,0:46:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.52,0:46:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't count because I needed
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.89,0:46:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.86,0:46:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I counted because it was the
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.50,0:46:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,first time in 22 years
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.78,0:46:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,that two entire surnames, cross
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.45,0:46:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and malvani.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.06,0:46:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sad in the same room without
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.35,0:46:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,anyone trying to defend
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.42,0:46:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,themselves from the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.98,0:46:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,His fingers moved slowly over
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.49,0:46:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the tabletop,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.64,0:46:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,without apparent purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.34,0:46:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Until they reached the edge of
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.62,0:46:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.50,0:46:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My fingers came to the other
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.93,0:46:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,end.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.62,0:46:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost without deciding.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.18,0:46:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Our thumbs came close to
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.37,0:46:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,touching.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.20,0:46:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They stopped there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.38,0:46:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Less than a centimeter apart
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.60,0:46:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,without touching.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.80,0:46:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not going to burn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.28,0:46:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.18,0:46:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He lifted his eyes with a
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.30,0:46:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,slowness that told me he already
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.73,0:46:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,knew I was going to say
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.24,0:47:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and was waiting anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.14,0:47:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to record him saying
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.82,0:47:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.34,0:47:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.38,0:47:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Everin stayed looking at me for
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.87,0:47:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.60,0:47:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Without asking how.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.12,0:47:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Without asking why.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.58,0:47:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.86,0:47:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In that way he'd had since the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.31,0:47:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,first time backstage at the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.61,0:47:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.54,0:47:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Months earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.68,0:47:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When he scanned the room's three
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.48,0:47:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,exits before scanning me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.12,0:47:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And then completely forgot the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.80,0:47:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,exits.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.80,0:47:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When he asked, there's day night
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.27,0:47:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.66,0:47:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll set up a private donors
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.91,0:47:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,event in the smaller ballroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.24,0:47:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,His allies will be invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.42,0:47:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll come because he always
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.58,0:47:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,comes to the hotel's events.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.08,0:47:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I lead it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.10,0:47:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.10,0:47:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.04,0:47:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario coordinates parallel
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.44,0:47:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,security.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.66,0:47:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir I works the catering.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.32,0:47:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I talk to Massimo in a side
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.79,0:47:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,room.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.54,0:47:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sealing microphones.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.98,0:47:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The old ones still installed
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.36,0:47:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,from last year's retrofit.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.04,0:47:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He nodded once.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.46,0:47:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.42,0:47:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.70,0:47:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The police move in on the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.75,0:47:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,warehouse when the confession is
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.09,0:47:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.94,0:47:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You go in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.04,0:47:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.40,0:47:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,To make sure she's alive when
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.03,0:47:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the door opens.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.38,0:48:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked at me for a long
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.71,0:48:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,while.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.34,0:48:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyes running over my face as
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.96,0:48:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,if searching for a fracture in
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.47,0:48:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the plan or in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.66,0:48:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what you're asking me
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.93,0:48:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.56,0:48:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.38,0:48:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to lose everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.00,0:48:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.92,0:48:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not asking you to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.78,0:48:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He said.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.76,0:48:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And his voice came out lower
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.96,0:48:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.18,0:48:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,With a layer underneath that
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.35,0:48:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.64,0:48:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.92,0:48:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking whether you truly
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.17,0:48:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,know what it means to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.54,0:48:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I stood up.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.62,0:48:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I rounded the table slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.96,0:48:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped in front of him and
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.43,0:48:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,put my hand on his face for the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.01,0:48:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,first time in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.74,0:48:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The skin was cold near the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.00,0:48:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.88,0:48:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Warm near the jaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.30,0:48:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He closed his eyes with the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.43,0:48:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,slowness of someone who had
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.57,0:48:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,forgotten what it was like to
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.79,0:48:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,receive
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.08,0:48:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that kind of touch without
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.29,0:48:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,having to prepare himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.86,0:48:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.86,0:48:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.94,0:48:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not going to burn my
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.31,0:48:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,father's truth to preserve your
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.83,0:48:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,father's empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.08,0:48:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're not going to ask me
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.72,0:48:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.10,0:48:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He opened his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.48,0:48:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.38,0:48:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He said.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.24,0:48:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I took my hand away slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.12,0:48:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I went back to the couch.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.22,0:48:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I picked up the events notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.81,0:48:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,from the coffee table.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.50,0:48:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Opened it to the first blank
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.98,0:49:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,page and started writing the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.46,0:49:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,guest list.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.48,0:49:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The names came easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.96,0:49:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,From memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.14,0:49:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I'd rehearsed them without
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.48,0:49:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,knowing for weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.90,0:49:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everin stood up.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.04,0:49:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He walked to the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.40,0:49:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He stayed with his back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.24,0:49:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hands crossed behind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.98,0:49:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at the lake darkening
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.22,0:49:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,with the last light of the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.33,0:49:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.44,0:49:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The horizon dissolving into blue
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.28,0:49:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.20,0:49:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.12,0:49:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He said.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.74,0:49:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Low.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.88,0:49:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Like someone sealing a pact with
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.51,0:49:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,himself out loud just to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.14,0:49:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,real.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.76,0:49:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.76,0:49:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.90,0:49:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Without lifting my head from the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.12,0:49:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.00,0:49:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The box stayed on top of the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.66,0:49:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,coffee table between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.32,0:49:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,With the packing tape on the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.63,0:49:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,edges intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.72,0:49:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And the names inside it waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.88,0:49:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither of us touched it that
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.13,0:49:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,night.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.64,0:49:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The hotel's smaller ballroom was
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.11,0:49:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,half the size of the main
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.25,0:49:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,ballroom and got double my
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.44,0:49:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.50,0:49:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew every exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.44,0:49:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Every outlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.76,0:49:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Every loose screw in the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.03,0:49:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,baseboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.56,0:49:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd chosen that space because it
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.41,0:49:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,was the only one in the hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.09,0:49:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,where I knew,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.06,0:50:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,by heart, where the sealing
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.61,0:50:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,microphones from the renovation
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.39,0:50:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,three years earlier were.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.14,0:50:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones that had never been
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.47,0:50:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,uninstalled.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.42,0:50:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Because no one on the board
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.62,0:50:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,remembered they existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.28,0:50:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.46,0:50:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I arrived at six in the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.69,0:50:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,afternoon with the private
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.07,0:50:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,donors events spreadsheet under
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.73,0:50:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,my arm,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.24,0:50:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,as if it were real.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.76,0:50:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was already setting up the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.25,0:50:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,buffet with the calm of someone
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.74,0:50:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,who'd never put a
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.56,0:50:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,spy earpiece in her ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.96,0:50:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,At least that was what she
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.37,0:50:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted to look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.88,0:50:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A canna pay is a bladed weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.10,0:50:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She said quietly when I passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.26,0:50:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever invented catering was
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.73,0:50:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,never at an event with this kind
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.35,0:50:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,of person.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.34,0:50:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.60,0:50:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm great.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.62,0:50:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm organizing a crime against a
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.24,0:50:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,mafia advisor while I serve
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.61,0:50:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,mushroom tartlets.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.06,0:50:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of question is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.76,0:50:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She laughed before finishing the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.27,0:50:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.24,0:50:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.26,0:50:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,For the first time all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.86,0:50:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It was only a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.34,0:50:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I needed that second.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.68,0:50:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria appeared through the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.01,0:50:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,service door in the same black
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.54,0:50:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,suit as always,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.66,0:50:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and two small bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.24,0:50:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He walked over to us with the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.60,0:50:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,manner of someone entering the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.01,0:50:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,ballroom for the 30th time that
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.47,0:50:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,day,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.02,0:51:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,even though he'd entered for the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.37,0:51:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,first.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.12,0:51:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He held out a small earpiece,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.83,0:51:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the color of syri skin,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.74,0:51:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and a microphone the size of a
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.99,0:51:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,lintel.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.44,0:51:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Dom. Ms. Dom.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.66,0:51:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Surai repeated, pretending to be
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.18,0:51:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.24,0:51:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.10,0:51:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm officially a spy
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.31,0:51:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.20,0:51:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I put that on my resume?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.38,0:51:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria looked at her for two and
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.08,0:51:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,a half seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.46,0:51:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You can.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.36,0:51:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That was all.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.52,0:51:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Surai opened her mouth, closed
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.45,0:51:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.90,0:51:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and filed the smile off to the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.36,0:51:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,side of her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.66,0:51:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.76,0:51:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She saw that I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.44,0:51:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria pretended not to see,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.26,0:51:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and still waited a millimeter
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.58,0:51:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,longer than necessary before
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.86,0:51:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,turning to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.84,0:51:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The ceiling microphones are
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.98,0:51:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,active.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.78,0:51:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The police move in when you give
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.14,0:51:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the signal with the agreed upon
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.46,0:51:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.28,0:51:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the night's going to run
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.61,0:51:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,long.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.28,0:51:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeated, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.74,0:51:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone came in through the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.26,0:51:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,service hallway at seven on the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.94,0:51:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.60,0:51:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't look at me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.14,0:51:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked at the exits.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.72,0:51:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The old habit I now knew how to
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.10,0:51:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,read,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.86,0:51:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and only then met my eyes across
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.44,0:51:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the ballroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.50,0:51:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,His hand went down to his pocket
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.03,0:51:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and stayed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.12,0:51:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.06,0:52:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd already noticed that the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.10,0:52:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,family ring had disappeared
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.10,0:52:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,from his finger since the day
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.50,0:52:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,before.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.24,0:52:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He hadn't said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.84,0:52:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither had I.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.98,0:52:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Massimo arrived at seven 15.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.98,0:52:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He came smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.24,0:52:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In the beige cashmere coat I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.73,0:52:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,already seen in a photo at the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.22,0:52:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,penthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.72,0:52:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the few in which everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.56,0:52:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,was a child in his arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.46,0:52:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He greeted three donors who
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.69,0:52:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,weren't donors as if greeting
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.00,0:52:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,distant relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.44,0:52:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He kissed my hand as if I were
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.96,0:52:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the hostess of a family tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.76,0:52:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Noelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.64,0:52:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, what a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.98,0:52:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Massimo, sit with me a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.22,0:52:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to walk you through the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.41,0:52:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,setup before the others arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.10,0:52:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.40,0:52:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The word dear landed on my skin
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.41,0:52:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,like a wet stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.00,0:52:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't flinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.06,0:52:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd practiced.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.08,0:52:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I took him to the sideroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.32,0:52:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The previous manager's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.86,0:52:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Old leather couch, round table,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.89,0:52:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,fake chandelier.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.54,0:52:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The ceiling microphones were
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.81,0:52:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,embedded in the stucco.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.44,0:52:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No one would look up.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.78,0:52:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I sat at the end of the couch.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.62,0:52:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He sat in the armchair across
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.96,0:52:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,from me and crossed his legs
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.25,0:52:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,like someone about to have
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.44,0:52:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.32,0:52:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever in his tents today.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.00,0:53:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He began.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.06,0:53:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Paternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.00,0:53:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This tape business is weighing
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.48,0:53:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.16,0:53:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I know my father was involved
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.42,0:53:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,with the old Melvani.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.02,0:53:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.00,0:53:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He was.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.00,0:53:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He sighed.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.78,0:53:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Antara was a good man in bad
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.25,0:53:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.72,0:53:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.02,0:53:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew him.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.06,0:53:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.06,0:53:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in the car with the old
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.30,0:53:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Melvani the night your father
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.55,0:53:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.52,0:53:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't expected the sentence
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.13,0:53:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.00,0:53:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt my pulse beat twice as
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.43,0:53:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,hard in my throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.78,0:53:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't blink.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.08,0:53:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.36,0:53:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.54,0:53:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.70,0:53:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Massimo uncrossed his legs and
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.22,0:53:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,rested his elbows on his knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.28,0:53:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You deserved to know Noelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.36,0:53:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He smiled as if he were doing a
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.10,0:53:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.44,0:53:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father was a sentimental
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.03,0:53:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,man in a place where sentiment
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.67,0:53:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,kills.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.66,0:53:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I resolved with the old Melvani
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.32,0:53:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,was too cowardly to resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.28,0:53:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.84,0:53:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I corrected a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.50,0:53:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't expect me to apologize for
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.11,0:53:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,something I kept standing for 20
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.72,0:53:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,years.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.50,0:53:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You would have done the same if
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.72,0:53:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd had the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.06,0:53:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The ceiling microphones were
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.34,0:53:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,capturing every syllable.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.10,0:53:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In Bruna, I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.14,0:54:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My voice low enough that he
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.36,0:54:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,leaned forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.68,0:54:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she now?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.92,0:54:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In a safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.80,0:54:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where nothing will happen to her
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.61,0:54:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,if Evern does as agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.48,0:54:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You kidnapped the mother of the
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.79,0:54:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,man who calls you father.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.40,0:54:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I borrowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.42,0:54:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.40,0:54:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The only leverage he has.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.24,0:54:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I breathed in deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.70,0:54:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at the chandelier.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.28,0:54:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I said calmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.64,0:54:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the night's going to run
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.11,0:54:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,long.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.78,0:54:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The sentence came out waitless.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.78,0:54:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Massimo didn't even register it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.70,0:54:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He kept talking about the old
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.92,0:54:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Melvani.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.88,0:54:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,About loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.26,0:54:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,About how Evern would still come
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.62,0:54:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.84,0:54:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was no longer listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.08,0:54:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere in the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.00,0:54:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario was closing the channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.72,0:54:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere in Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.24,0:54:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Two federal police cars were
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.59,0:54:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,pulling out of a garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.34,0:54:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere above our heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.04,0:54:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A fake chandelier was recording
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.58,0:54:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the complete confession of
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.87,0:54:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Massimo Grel.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.04,0:54:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That was when he saw my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.02,0:54:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what appeared in
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.40,0:54:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.82,0:54:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the lack of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.52,0:54:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He stood up in half a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.10,0:54:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And his hand was on my wrist
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.35,0:54:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,while the other went to the
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.55,0:54:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,pocket of his beige coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.12,0:54:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He knew the police already had
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.51,0:54:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the audio.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.48,0:55:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He knew he had minutes, not
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.02,0:55:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.36,0:55:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do, Noelia?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.60,0:55:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The gun pressed against the side
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.12,0:55:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.94,0:55:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Low, hidden by the couch.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.96,0:55:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt the cold metal through my
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.61,0:55:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.32,0:55:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.66,0:55:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You recorded it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.92,0:55:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He said.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.86,0:55:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I recorded it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.12,0:55:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The door of the side room opened
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.61,0:55:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,without a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.90,0:55:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario was standing in it with
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.25,0:55:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that half expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.86,0:55:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Less neutral than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.68,0:55:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That he kept for emergencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.38,0:55:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't look at Massimo.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.94,0:55:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.08,0:55:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.36,0:55:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Massimo stepped back.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.86,0:55:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The gun lowered.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.46,0:55:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He let go of my wrist slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.34,0:55:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Unhurried.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.10,0:55:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Calculating something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.80,0:55:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew what he was calculating.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.70,0:55:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The parking garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.08,0:55:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Runa.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.94,0:55:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He said.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.78,0:55:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was the only word before
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.98,0:55:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,he left through the back door
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.10,0:55:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,toward the service hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.64,0:55:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario looked at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.88,0:55:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I shook my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.12,0:55:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He went after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.34,0:55:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I stayed in the armchair for
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.50,0:55:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,four seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.60,0:55:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I counted.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.70,0:55:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Four seconds for my pulse to
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.94,0:55:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,return to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.04,0:55:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I got up.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.36,0:55:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the main door.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.74,0:55:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And cross the ballroom holding
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.21,0:56:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the fake event spreadsheet under
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.78,0:56:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.12,0:56:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,As if it were still real.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.10,0:56:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So I looked at me from across
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.53,0:56:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.38,0:56:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.54,0:56:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She asked with only her mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.44,0:56:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.54,0:56:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She exhaled.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.76,0:56:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It was only at that instant that
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.24,0:56:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed she'd been holding her
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.71,0:56:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,breath since Massimo walked
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.96,0:56:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,into the side room.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.24,0:56:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The warehouse by the lake was
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.89,0:56:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,made of galvanized sheet metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.02,0:56:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Had a rusty sliding gate and
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.94,0:56:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,smelled of old motor oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.22,0:56:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.42,0:56:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It had been a family part's
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.15,0:56:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,depot in the 90s.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.54,0:56:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Massimo had never brought me
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.82,0:56:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,there.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.10,0:56:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I understood why.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.42,0:56:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I went in alone as arranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.20,0:56:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario had stayed 200 meters away
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.33,0:56:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,in the car with the federal
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.12,0:56:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,police two turns from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.32,0:56:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The flash drive of the recording
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.02,0:56:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Noelia had just made was in my
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.61,0:56:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,inner pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.78,0:56:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Over my chest, Massimo was in
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.64,0:56:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the middle of the warehouse
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.37,0:56:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,under a single yellow lamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.58,0:56:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Two armed men, one on each side.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.58,0:56:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother was tied to a wooden
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.40,0:56:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,chair three meters from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.10,0:57:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A live, no bruise in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.06,0:57:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Her gaze met mine for a second
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.93,0:57:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and I recognized that
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.24,0:57:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.50,0:57:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the same one she'd had
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.98,0:57:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,after my father died.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.54,0:57:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.58,0:57:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do anything stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.20,0:57:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You came fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.70,0:57:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Massimo said, you called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.06,0:57:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought the flash drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.84,0:57:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I took it out of my pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.60,0:57:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I placed it on my open palm.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.80,0:57:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Massimo looked at it with his
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.34,0:57:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,usual tired tenderness.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.56,0:57:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And I, for the first time in 20
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.98,0:57:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,years saw that tenderness for
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.24,0:57:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.98,0:57:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.18,0:57:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.20,0:57:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He said.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.86,0:57:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,First you say in front of these
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.42,0:57:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,two men, what you ordered done.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.36,0:57:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The two henchmen I'd each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.96,0:57:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Massimo laughed low.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.46,0:57:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sentimental.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.06,0:57:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.22,0:57:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.16,0:57:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He sighed.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.34,0:57:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked at my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.88,0:57:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.00,0:57:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, with the patience of
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.76,0:57:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,someone who'd never been
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.22,0:57:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,contradicted by me in 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.56,0:57:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed Antero Cross because he
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.24,0:57:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,was going to bring the house
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.72,0:57:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,down.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.36,0:57:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I set up the ambush that killed
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.01,0:58:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,your father because the old
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.44,0:58:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Malvani was going soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.14,0:58:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I raised you because you were
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.61,0:58:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,more useful alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.20,0:58:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.06,0:58:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Break the flash drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.74,0:58:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The two henchmen stopped
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.80,0:58:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.74,0:58:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at them long enough for
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.30,0:58:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,them to see my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.70,0:58:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And understand that I'd heard
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.10,0:58:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the same sentence they had.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.78,0:58:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I took the ring out of my
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.18,0:58:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,pants pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.32,0:58:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The crest of an eagle with
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.04,0:58:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,folded wings, old gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.56,0:58:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Three Melvani generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.22,0:58:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I set it on top of a crate
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.95,0:58:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,beside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.90,0:58:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Melvani ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.46,0:58:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, out loud to the two men.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.86,0:58:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever stays with me walks out
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.70,0:58:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.62,0:58:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever stays with him chooses.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.10,0:58:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew what I'd just done.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.88,0:58:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In two sentences, I dissolved 20
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.08,0:58:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,years of structure.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.98,0:58:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt nothing heroic.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.58,0:58:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt the way you feel when you
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.20,0:58:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,sat down a very heavy suitcase
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.72,0:58:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you didn't even remember
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.94,0:58:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you were carrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.64,0:58:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The two henchmen lowered their
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.52,0:58:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,guns in half a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.50,0:58:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That was all.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.84,0:58:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Massimo opened his mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.46,0:58:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.70,0:58:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The warehouse door opened from
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.20,0:58:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.46,0:59:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario first, federal police
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.40,0:59:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.50,0:59:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Massimo raised his hands without
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.97,0:59:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,needing to be told.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.34,0:59:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The man had seen this happen to
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.75,0:59:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,too many people not to know the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.17,0:59:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,choreography.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.46,0:59:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother closed her eyes for a
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.20,0:59:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,second and breathed.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.42,0:59:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.66,0:59:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I untied the rope from her wrist
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.27,0:59:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,with my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.36,0:59:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My hands were shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.42,0:59:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed it for the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.47,0:59:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.46,0:59:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You took your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.90,0:59:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She said quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.48,0:59:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.26,0:59:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a criticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.98,0:59:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I pressed my forehead to hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.04,0:59:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,For two seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.54,0:59:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough for an entire lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.62,0:59:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The flash drive was still in my
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.17,0:59:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.84,0:59:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The penthouse was in silence
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.11,0:59:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,when he arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.30,0:59:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd turned off all the lights
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.66,0:59:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,except the living room lamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.50,0:59:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And Lake Michigan down below.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.68,0:59:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,looked like a black sheet with
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.11,0:59:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,small bites of old gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.78,0:59:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Bruno was in her own mother's
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.88,0:59:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.74,0:59:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.66,0:59:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,With Dario outside since
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.04,0:59:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.16,0:59:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Massimo had been in federal
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.55,0:59:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,custody since 115.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.26,0:59:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd turned off my phone after
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.74,0:59:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorai confirmed it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.36,0:59:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever and came in through the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.56,0:59:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,internal staircase door.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.06,1:00:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at his right hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.68,1:00:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The ring wasn't anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.34,1:00:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.54,1:00:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He said.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.48,1:00:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.26,1:00:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He crossed the room slowly and
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.91,1:00:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped to step away from me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.72,1:00:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a little motor oil on
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.12,1:00:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,his shirt cuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.14,1:00:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And the mark of the jute rope on
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.55,1:00:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the edge of his left hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.10,1:00:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,From where he'd freed his
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.12,1:00:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,mother's wrist.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.74,1:00:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed it before anything
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.78,1:00:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,else.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.40,1:00:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first time in three
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.28,1:00:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,months that I looked at his
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.97,1:00:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,hands and didn't see a man who
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.85,1:00:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,knew
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.10,1:00:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,where the exits were.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.60,1:00:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a man who had just freed
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.96,1:00:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,his mother from a chair.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.50,1:00:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I turned everything in.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.90,1:00:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He said.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.90,1:00:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The police have the flash drive.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.68,1:00:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They have your father's tape.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.46,1:00:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They have the confession.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.02,1:00:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The Melvani is over.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.72,1:00:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.54,1:00:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He stayed still.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.76,1:00:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was only at that instant
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.12,1:00:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that I noticed he was waiting
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.39,1:00:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,for me to take the step.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.94,1:00:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For me to choose.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.80,1:00:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.30,1:00:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I placed my hand on his chest.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.08,1:00:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,On the left side.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.32,1:00:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the inner pocket where the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.67,1:00:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,flash drive had been.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.04,1:00:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt his heartbeat twice
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.35,1:00:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,against my palm.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.66,1:00:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Take off your shirt.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.00,1:00:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't laugh.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.26,1:00:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't joke.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.50,1:00:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He lifted his hand to the first
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.81,1:01:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,button.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.62,1:01:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.36,1:01:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I said.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.28,1:01:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take it off.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.44,1:01:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I started at the second button.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.24,1:01:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My fingers weren't shaking.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.92,1:01:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine weren't.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.04,1:01:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,His were.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.98,1:01:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never seen ever in his hand
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.32,1:01:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,shake.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.04,1:01:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt the warmth of his skin
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.51,1:01:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,before the shirt even fell.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.88,1:01:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was the first thing
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.59,1:01:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that undid me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.72,1:01:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Not his beauty, which I already
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.64,1:01:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,knew by heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.00,1:01:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The warmth.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.98,1:01:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The realization that he was
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.61,1:01:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,there, alive, standing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.68,1:01:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a family name.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.40,1:01:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.32,1:01:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Elia.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.44,1:01:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, low.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.48,1:01:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.62,1:01:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The shirt fell to the living
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.83,1:01:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,room floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.82,1:01:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The tattoos on his arms were
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.36,1:01:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,old.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.02,1:01:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,With no crest at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.60,1:01:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I already knew them.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.00,1:01:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But that night they seemed like
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.33,1:01:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,something else.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.34,1:01:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They seemed for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.36,1:01:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Only his.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.96,1:01:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He picked me up with the calm
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.53,1:01:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,urgency of a man who'd spent the
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.27,1:01:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,whole night holding
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.30,1:01:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,his captive mother, holding his
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.35,1:01:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,own father dead for 20 years,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.58,1:01:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,holding a ring that weighed
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.82,1:01:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,three generations.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.32,1:01:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And now didn't want to hold
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.56,1:01:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,anything other than me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.88,1:01:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He crossed the room toward the
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.17,1:01:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.10,1:02:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I pressed my mouth to the side
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.52,1:02:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of his neck and felt his pulse
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.94,1:02:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,beat against my lips.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.44,1:02:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the same rhythm as months
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.05,1:02:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,before.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.90,1:02:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,On the hotel balcony.
