Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.22,1:12:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd told the story three times
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.57,1:12:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,at the dinner the night before.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.36,1:12:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And gotten teary-eyed all.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.54,1:12:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.92,1:12:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tisha Rome, at the back,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.75,1:12:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,discreet.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.00,1:12:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Her hair now short and her eyes
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.65,1:12:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,without any makeup.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.22,1:12:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd testified against Calvin
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.68,1:12:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,seven months earlier.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.22,1:12:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Had moved to another city for
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.61,1:12:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,three months.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.74,1:12:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd come back a different
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.75,1:12:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.42,1:12:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd sent a note the week
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.68,1:12:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,before asking to be there.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.18,1:12:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I said yes without needing to
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.69,1:12:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,think.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.56,1:12:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvin wasn't mentioned by
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.79,1:12:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.58,1:12:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd been convicted months
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.88,1:12:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,earlier to six years for the
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.28,1:12:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,campaign and bezelmen.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.66,1:13:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus more things that turned up
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.00,1:13:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,after the first stone rolled.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.26,1:13:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd seen the headline on an
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.74,1:13:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,airport bench once, coming back
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.44,1:13:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,from San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.14,1:13:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked for two seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.72,1:13:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept walking.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.08,1:13:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Everand was on the other side of
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.17,1:13:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the balcony.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.22,1:13:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Black suit, no tie, no ring on
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.25,1:13:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,his right finger.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.88,1:13:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd never put another ring
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.93,1:13:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,there since the night at the
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.01,1:13:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.92,1:13:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd said the week before that
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.50,1:13:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,he was going to put the wedding
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.14,1:13:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,band on the left,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.46,1:13:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and that that was already enough
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.74,1:13:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,for an entire lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.20,1:13:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't argue.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.44,1:13:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario was beside him.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.94,1:13:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Black suit too.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.28,1:13:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Black tie.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.88,1:13:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Neutral expression as always.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.68,1:13:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Surai nudged my elbow.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.32,1:13:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at him.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.26,1:13:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She whispered.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.40,1:13:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dressed just like the cemetery
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.82,1:13:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,suit.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.72,1:13:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Surai.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.58,1:13:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A poorly wrapped problem is
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.98,1:13:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,hereditary noelia.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.54,1:13:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I pressed my lips together so I
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.90,1:13:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't laugh.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.08,1:13:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She pressed hers together too.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.94,1:13:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,For two seconds, the two of us
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.52,1:13:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,looked like two teenagers in a
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.11,1:13:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,school line.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.18,1:13:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Holding back the laugh with our
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.41,1:13:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,hands over our mouths.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.76,1:13:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I walked over to Everand.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.44,1:13:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He hadn't moved his face.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.02,1:14:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But I saw, when I got close,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.06,1:14:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,his pulse beat twice as hard on
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.75,1:14:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the side of his neck.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.40,1:14:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd known how to read that in
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.68,1:14:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,him for years.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.76,1:14:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The one sign he couldn't
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.74,1:14:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,control.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.62,1:14:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,His vow was short.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.90,1:14:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd asked him not to write much.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.84,1:14:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He complied.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.94,1:14:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised on the balcony where
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.35,1:14:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,we're standing a year ago
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.48,1:14:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that I wouldn't lie to you
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.57,1:14:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.38,1:14:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.56,1:14:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep keeping it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.76,1:14:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.64,1:14:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That was everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.98,1:14:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine was a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.56,1:14:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Not much.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.54,1:14:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I arrived at this hotel one
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.83,1:14:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,night believing I'd hired an
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.16,1:14:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,escort by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.50,1:14:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I left believing I'd made a
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.71,1:14:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,mistake that would cost me
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.88,1:14:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,it took me three months to
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.43,1:14:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,understand I'd made a mistake in
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.35,1:14:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,a way that had given me
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.72,1:14:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,everything back.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.02,1:14:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at him.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.18,1:14:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The night the hotel's big screen
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.69,1:14:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,decided for us was the luckiest
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.16,1:14:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,night of my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.20,1:14:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I just didn't know it yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.80,1:14:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He lowered his head for half a
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.03,1:14:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,second.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.84,1:14:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw his cheek go darker.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.82,1:14:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Bruna in the first row brought a
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.75,1:14:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,handkerchief to her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.76,1:14:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrised sniffled.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.98,1:14:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario tightened his tie with two
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.54,1:14:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,fingers and let go slowly.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.40,1:14:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The judge said the line.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.04,1:14:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Everand kissed me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.00,1:14:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a simple kiss.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.02,1:15:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.84,1:15:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,With no hurry at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.42,1:15:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No one to beat.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.26,1:15:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to prove.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.76,1:15:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrised whispered in my ear
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.89,1:15:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,when I went back to the row.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.56,1:15:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.30,1:15:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're a poorly wrapped
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.59,1:15:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,problem too.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.52,1:15:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I laughed.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.60,1:15:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This time I laughed first.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.30,1:15:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We bought the house on the lake
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.56,1:15:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in our fifth year of marriage.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.06,1:15:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It had a large living room with
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.53,1:15:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,a high ceiling and light that
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.90,1:15:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,came in until the middle of the
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.37,1:15:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.46,1:15:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A kitchen with a window facing
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.85,1:15:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the water where the smell of
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.15,1:15:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,coffee always mixed with the
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.45,1:15:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,smell
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.68,1:15:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,of wet grass coming from the
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.06,1:15:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,garden.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.40,1:15:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And two small bedrooms upstairs,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.00,1:15:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,side by side.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.60,1:15:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We're before nothing had lived.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.32,1:15:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now too lived there.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.80,1:15:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl was four years old and
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.57,1:15:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,had her father's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.22,1:15:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark, attentive.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.98,1:15:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind that noticed everything
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.38,1:15:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,before asking anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.84,1:15:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy was too and had my
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.59,1:15:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,father's laugh.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.92,1:15:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Something I didn't know he'd
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.11,1:15:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,inherited until he laughed for
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.39,1:15:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the first time in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.90,1:15:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the laugh I hadn't heard
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.32,1:15:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,since I was seven years old.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.86,1:15:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I stood there with the towel in
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.46,1:15:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,my hand too long.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.34,1:15:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And everyone appeared in the
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.79,1:15:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,doorway and looked at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.30,1:15:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And didn't ask anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.84,1:16:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And stayed there until I
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.86,1:16:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,breathed again.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.98,1:16:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The events company had opened in
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.57,1:16:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the second year.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.64,1:16:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd named it in my father's
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.89,1:16:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,honor without telling anyone it
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.34,1:16:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,was an honor.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.42,1:16:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Only Sarai knew.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.74,1:16:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.80,1:16:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The first client was a
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.83,1:16:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,42-year-old woman who had been
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.24,1:16:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,left at the altar at the Hilton
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.70,1:16:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,in Houston three months earlier.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.74,1:16:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I organized her birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.80,1:16:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,300 people.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.18,1:16:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She danced all night with her
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.70,1:16:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,shoes in her hand from midnight
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.32,1:16:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,on.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.48,1:16:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end she hugged me at the
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.15,1:16:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,door and said,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.16,1:16:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know what I needed?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.82,1:16:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I knew.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.72,1:16:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't ask anything else.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.80,1:16:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sarai was a partner, officially,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.48,1:16:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,from the third year on.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.06,1:16:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario showed up at the office
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.42,1:16:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,with suspicious frequency,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.38,1:16:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,always with coffee from the
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.80,1:16:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,bakery Sarai liked,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.22,1:16:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and the two still pretended no
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.58,1:16:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,one noticed.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.34,1:16:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sarai said it had been the worst
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.80,1:16:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,mistake of her life,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.96,1:16:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and the only one she'd make
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.17,1:16:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,again.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.50,1:16:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario answered with a half
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.78,1:16:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,expression.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.16,1:16:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She filed the smile away.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.38,1:16:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She always filed it away.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.18,1:16:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If Ren managed to completely
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.69,1:16:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,legal operations,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.34,1:17:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,one in hospitality in Chicago,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.44,1:17:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,another in freight transport in
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.78,1:17:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Detroit.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.10,1:17:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no one calling him sir
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.57,1:17:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.88,1:17:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no one waiting for him
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.39,1:17:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,to decide something without
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.66,1:17:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,asking his wife first.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.88,1:17:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He used to say,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.24,1:17:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When the new partners asked how
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.52,1:17:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd learned to delegate,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.16,1:17:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that it had been the hard way,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.95,1:17:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,no one understood, I understood.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.86,1:17:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The garden in late spring turned
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.82,1:17:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,green nearly yellow in the late
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.73,1:17:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.94,1:17:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sitting on the wooden step
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.44,1:17:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of the deck.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.28,1:17:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My bare feet against the grass
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.82,1:17:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,still damp from the morning
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.21,1:17:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,sprinkler,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.22,1:17:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and I watched the two of them
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.59,1:17:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,run around the bucket of water
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.00,1:17:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and Oliya had filled at
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.17,1:17:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,lunchtime.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.08,1:17:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl always won.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.88,1:17:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy laughed even losing.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.90,1:17:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,At some moments she'd come back
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.54,1:17:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,to push him lightly before
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.91,1:17:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,continuing to run,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.14,1:17:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and he'd laugh again, and they'd
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.82,1:17:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,keep going,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.70,1:17:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and the sequence repeated in a
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.24,1:17:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,loop,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.50,1:17:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,as if that garden were the only
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.20,1:17:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,place in the world where it made
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.95,1:17:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,sense to stay,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.36,1:17:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought without warning, of my
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.31,1:17:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,father.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.30,1:17:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not of what he'd been, of what
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.80,1:17:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,he would have been if Masimo
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.19,1:18:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,hadn't decided otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.04,1:18:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,20 odd years earlier.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.84,1:18:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought of on Tero too.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.50,1:18:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought of him many times in
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.06,1:18:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the last seven years.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.60,1:18:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first time I'd
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.82,1:18:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,thought of him without wait,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.74,1:18:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,only with gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.18,1:18:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought of the old Malvani for
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.86,1:18:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,half a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.94,1:18:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought of Masimo for less.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.60,1:18:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of them were in the same
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.72,1:18:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,place now.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.66,1:18:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In packages I'd stored in some
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.23,1:18:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,compartment of my head and
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.60,1:18:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,locked with a key.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.86,1:18:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to forget, so I wouldn't
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.42,1:18:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,have to open it every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.22,1:18:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl fell in the grass.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.10,1:18:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She got up without crying, she
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.50,1:18:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,kept running.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.42,1:18:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd spent the first 36 years of
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.38,1:18:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,my life believing that being
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.15,1:18:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,seen was being exposed.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.20,1:18:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That a man standing didn't lower
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.94,1:18:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,his guard.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.98,1:18:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That sentiment was the first
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.58,1:18:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,thing the enemy used to take you
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.41,1:18:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,down.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.70,1:18:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman had walked into the
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.35,1:18:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,hotel one night thinking she was
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.10,1:18:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,hiring an accessory.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.60,1:18:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Had looked me in the eye without
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.15,1:18:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,knowing who I was,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.30,1:18:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and had kept looking at me after
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.96,1:18:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,finding out.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.92,1:18:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the only thing in my
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.70,1:18:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,entire life that had taught me
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.68,1:18:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.04,1:19:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Being seen without lying was the
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.73,1:19:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,only way to be loved.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.34,1:19:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It had taken me almost 40 years
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.94,1:19:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to understand a sentence of
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.34,1:19:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,eight words.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.48,1:19:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I smelled the coffee before I
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.05,1:19:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,turned my head.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.28,1:19:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I crossed the garden with two
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.73,1:19:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,cups.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.98,1:19:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The one on the left had sugar,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.75,1:19:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the one on the right didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.68,1:19:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I never switched them.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.04,1:19:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In seven years I hadn't switched
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.73,1:19:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,ones, and he'd never asked me to
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.41,1:19:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,switch.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.28,1:19:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I sat beside him on the step.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.16,1:19:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The wood was warm from the
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.45,1:19:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,afternoon sun.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.54,1:19:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I held out the one without
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.74,1:19:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,sugar.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.52,1:19:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He accepted it without looking
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.81,1:19:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,at the cup.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.54,1:19:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked at me first, as he
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.45,1:19:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,always did,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.62,1:19:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,as if I were the most important
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.17,1:19:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,information before anything
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.53,1:19:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,else.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.10,1:19:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to sleep in the
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.23,1:19:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,car today.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.10,1:19:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, they always sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.40,1:19:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl fell again.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.32,1:19:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She got up again.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.22,1:19:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shook the dirt off her knee with
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.55,1:19:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,two efficient slaps.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.96,1:19:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy sat in the middle of the
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.29,1:19:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,grass.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.98,1:19:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Decided he was tired, and
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.22,1:19:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,started pulling up toughs with
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.71,1:19:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the tranquil patients of someone
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.29,1:19:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,who
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.44,1:19:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,had the rest of his life to do
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.97,1:19:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.30,1:19:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I leaned my shoulder against a
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.68,1:19:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,vr. shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.74,1:19:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He leaned his shoulder against
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.08,1:19:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.68,1:19:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the oldest gesture in our
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.31,1:19:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,house.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.90,1:20:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Older than the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.34,1:20:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd learned it from him on the
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.94,1:20:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,penthouse balcony in the third
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.54,1:20:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,month.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.24,1:20:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,On a night when I didn't want to
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.93,1:20:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,talk, and he hadn't insisted on
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.58,1:20:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,talking.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.00,1:20:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd stayed like that, shoulder
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.09,1:20:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to shoulder,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.56,1:20:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,until the sky brightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.20,1:20:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I took a sip.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.36,1:20:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The coffee was strong, a little
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.17,1:20:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,bitter,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.16,1:20:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly the way I liked it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.88,1:20:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, without meaning to,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.68,1:20:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,of a sentence I'd said to myself
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.60,1:20:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,seven years earlier,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.24,1:20:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,in a low voice, at the entrance
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.03,1:20:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,of my old department.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.86,1:20:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The morning after the first
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.16,1:20:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,kiss,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.66,1:20:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd said it was strange to know
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.14,1:20:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,so little of the past of someone
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.67,1:20:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd just chosen to believe in.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.38,1:20:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I knew everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.40,1:20:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd known too soon afterward,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.32,1:20:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and it had hurt more than
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.79,1:20:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,anything before, but I knew.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.94,1:20:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And knowing hadn't undone the
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.41,1:20:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.26,1:20:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It had sustained it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.72,1:20:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I watched the boy pulling up
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.05,1:20:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,grass with the concentration of
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.51,1:20:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,a scientist.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.66,1:20:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I watched the girl counting her
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.22,1:20:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,own steps out loud.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.80,1:20:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Four, five, six.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.72,1:20:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Always starting over at seven.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.70,1:20:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at the lake at the end
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.87,1:20:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of the garden.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.92,1:21:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's silvery surface against the
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.37,1:21:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,sky that was starting to turn
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.69,1:21:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,orange at the edges.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.60,1:21:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of color that lasted a
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.64,1:21:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,short time,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.70,1:21:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and that you only saw when you
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.82,1:21:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,were looking.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.92,1:21:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dignity, I thought, wasn't never
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.13,1:21:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,falling.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.28,1:21:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I had fallen.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.62,1:21:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd fallen at the altar at 20
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.18,1:21:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,odd years old,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.26,1:21:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,before 200 people who preferred
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.07,1:21:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to pity me, then to defend me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.00,1:21:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd fallen again in the hotel
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.66,1:21:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,ballroom three months after the
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.43,1:21:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,first kiss.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.34,1:21:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When I heard my father's voice
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.79,1:21:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,come out of a 20-year-old tape,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.72,1:21:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd fallen every time I needed
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.28,1:21:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to fall,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.02,1:21:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and gotten up without asking
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.38,1:21:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,permission for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.26,1:21:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Dignity was getting up and
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.85,1:21:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,building a house where pain had
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.75,1:21:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,no way in.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.62,1:21:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The house was all around.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.24,1:21:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The children were in the garden.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.90,1:21:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The man was at my side.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.46,1:21:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,His shoulder against mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.10,1:21:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,With no family rang at all on
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.64,1:21:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,his finger,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.76,1:21:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,holding a cup of coffee without
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.23,1:21:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,sugar,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.08,1:21:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,as if it were the simplest and
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.43,1:21:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,most certain thing in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.26,1:21:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I took the second sip, and I
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.13,1:21:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,smiled.